data.description: Charming 3/4 bedroom Home a moments from renovated Marilla Park! This home provides quick access to I-68 and downtown, and features an updated kitchen and open floor plan ideal for entertaining. The finished lower level den with a full bath adds extra space, while the second story boasts a large primary bedroom, additional bedrooms, and laundry. This home checks so many boxes for those looking for a move in ready home with extras!
